{
  "_comment": "AXM Genesis v1 identity vectors (spec/v1/SPECIFICATION.md section 10). canonicalize() = (1) NFC, (2) ASCII-only lowering A-Z->a-z, (3) strip category-Cc control characters, (4) collapse frozen-set whitespace runs to one ASCII space and trim. IDs = prefix + base32lower(SHA-256(preimage)) over the full 32-byte digest, no padding: 52 base32 chars after e1_/c1_/p1_/s1_. Generated by the v1 reference kernel and independently spot-checked from the spec definition.",
